<AbstractNarration>0098429&lt;br/&gt;Mermin&lt;br/&gt;The PI will re-examine old interpretational questions in the foundations of quantum mechanics in the light of new developments in quantum computation which focus on the quantum state exclusively as a way of manipulating of transmitting (digital) information.&lt;br/&gt;A self-contained introduction to the quantum theory will be formulated that is entirely accessible to computer scientists unacquainted with contemporary physics, as a generalization of how one defines and manipulates the ordinary bits of classical information theory.&lt;br/&gt;</AbstractNarration>
